    "causal_summary": "Devin CLI orchestrator enabling any AI assistant to invoke Cognition AI's official Devin for Terminal (Rust binary) for autonomous coding work, with the unique capability of local-to-cloud handoff: a local devin session can delegate to a cloud-hosted Devin VM that keeps working after the laptop closes and returns a PR. This skill makes Devin a peer executor in the cli-* family so any of the four sibling skills (cli-claude-code, cli-codex, cli-gemini, cli-opencode) can dispatch to Devin via the same orchestration contract.",
